name: The End of the Line
description:
Ink on paper – 5000x5000px
Detail of Estacion del Mago.

The end of the line is this area where the state decided to stop, and the begining of the wild side, also the perfect place to paint the line. 
The Yacumama is around, coming out of the Rimac river looking over the goods dragged by the mudslides.

*Collect 1 only, together with the next 2 objkts to be released and get the full piece.
Thank You
